Race.SpecificTitle: Town of Columbia -- 3 Mills - TC - 10 Yrs.
Race.FullText: Shall the Town of Columbia, State of Louisiana, (the "Town"), be authorized to levy a special tax of three (3) mills on all property subject to taxation within the Town, (an estimated $12,101.00 expected at this time to be collected from the levy of the tax for an entire year), for a period of ten (10) years, beginning with the year 2015 and ending with the year 2024, for the purpose of constructing, maintaining and improving public streets within and for the Town?
